    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **Host**: 先看 CPU、内存、load、磁盘 IO、网络 IO，判断是不是机器层资源问题。\n- **Redis**: 重点看 ops、hit rate、evictions、fragmentation、slowlog、clients，确认缓存是否在拖慢 Search / AI。\n- **PostgreSQL**: 重点看连接数、TPS、lock waits、deadlocks、cache hit ratio，确认是不是 DB 在拖慢 Search / Import。\n- **Use Together**: 业务链路抖动时，先回到这里看底层资源是否同步异常。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "主机 CPU 利用率，范围 0-1。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 2,
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm:node_cpu_utilization:ratio5m",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
